Johanita Scholtz (ka amụrụ na 25 Jenụwarị 2000) bụ onye egwuregwu badminton nke South Africa. Scholtz meriri aha mbụ ya na mba ụwa na asọmpi Botswana International nke afọ 2017. Ọ sọrọ mpi na 2018 Commonwealth Games na Gold Coast, Australia. Ọ bụ onye nrite ọla edo nke ụmụ nwanyị na 2019 African Games, nwetakwara ọla nchara na otu na ụmụ nwanyị abụọ.
